      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, currently maintained to a showroom standard that defies its previous ownership. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, odor-free cabin\u2014reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and responsiveness of a factory-new unit. This is an acquisition for the discerning driver who demands unrivaled quality and aesthetic perfection.",
