    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to be passing this beauty along to its next owner. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and it looks just as gorgeous as the day I bought it. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you've found it. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
